                    <p rend="center"><hi rend="smallcaps">receipts</hi>.</p>
                    <p>The various sources of revenue are estimated as follows: <table cols="2" rows="19">
                            <row>
                                <cell>Tax on real property</cell>
                                <cell role="num">$36,000,000</cell>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <cell>Industry and trade</cell>
                                <cell role="num">8,000,000</cell>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <cell>Transfers of lands, &amp;c</cell>
                                <cell role="num">6,200,000</cell>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <cell>Consular fees</cell>
                                <cell role="num">455,000</cell>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <cell>Nobility fees</cell>
                                <cell role="num">140,000</cell>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <cell>Poll tax</cell>
