                        </table></p>
                    <pb facs="0852" n="724" xml:id="pg_724"/>
                    <p>The official statement will be found in the Gaceta de Madrid, No. 176, June
                        25, 1885, on file in the library of the Department of State.</p>
                    <p>I am, &amp;c.,</p>
                    <closer><signed>JOHN W. FOSTER.</signed></closer>
